summary: SUB FRAME FROM MAIN FRAME TO OUTSIDE EDGE IS FAILING.  METAL IS BENDING AND CRACKING CAUSING THE WALLS TO SAG.  WELDS ARE NOT COMPLETE IN SOME AREAS.  SUB-FRAME IS SAGGING APPROXIMATELY 1/4 TO 1/2 INCH. OVER ABOUT 12 INCH SPAN.  FAILURE IS MOST NOTICEABLE IN FRONT OF AND BEHIND THE WHEEL WELL AREA .  (TANDEM AXLE TRAILER)   WE HAVE A FILE OF PHOTOS.    THE CONSUMER REQUESTED INFORMATION INTO 13 COMPLAINTS PERTAINING TO TRAILERS WITH A FAILING FRAME STRUCTURE. *JS
